snippet.title: The "Catacombs" | Announcement Trailer (Indie Horror Game)
snippet.description:
! Warning Flashing Lights !
Play the game here:
https://pinwormdev.itch.io/the-catacombs

The "Catacombs" is an indie horror game developed by Pinworm.
Coming to Itch.io on the 15th Of July 2022


Game Description:
"a 3d horror game in which you are exploring the catacombs of Paris through the lens of a VHS camcorder. The game was inspired by found footage of a man seemingly lost in the catacombs."


Games - https://pinwormdev.itch.io/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/PinwormDev


More gameplay information will be released soon.
#indiegame #gaming #thriller
